{"tid":2217110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧下周訪問梵蒂岡","createTime":"2020-09-25T07:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T14:35:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":148,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"fc022f0bf24408666d594e51350c0a687864e430","tid":2217110,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/09/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E6%A2%B5%E8%92%82%E5%B2%A1-20200925120006_217f_large.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F09%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7-%25E6%25A2%25B5%25E8%2592%2582%25E5%25B2%25A1-20200925120006_217f_large.png&h=7de83254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院的聲明指，蓬佩奧將於9月27日到10月2日訪問希臘、意大利、梵蒂岡及克羅地亞。訪問梵蒂岡時，蓬佩奧將在「外交推動及捍衛宗教自由教廷論壇」（Holy See Symposium on Advancing and Defending Religious Freedom through Diplomacy）發言。聲明又稱，蓬佩奧將會晤教廷國務卿帕羅林（Secretary of State Cardinal Parolin）以及教廷外長加拉查（Secretary for Relations with States Archbishop Gallagher）。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧出訪梵蒂岡之前，本月20日在Twitter轉發他在宗教刊物《第一要務》（First Things）的文章 〈中國天主教徒與教會的道德見證〉 ( China&rsquo;s Catholics and The Church&rsquo;s Moral Witness) ，指中國人權狀況嚴重惡化，宗教信徒受害，中梵簽署主教任命臨時協議兩年後，顯然協議並未能令天主教徒免受蹂躪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/34217/%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E6%A2%B5%E8%92%82%E5%B2%A1-34217/%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E8%A8%AA%E6%A2%B5%E8%92%82%E5%B2%A1%E6%99%A4%E6%95%99%E5%BB%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E5%8D%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F34217%2F%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7-%25E6%25A2%25B5%25E8%2592%2582%25E5%25B2%25A1-34217%2F%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%25A2%25B5%25E8%2592%2582%25E5%25B2%25A1%25E6%2599%25A4%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%258D%25BF&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzvUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=04d0ee5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/34217/%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E6%A2%B5%E8%92%82%E5%B2%A1-34217/%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E8%A8%AA%E6%A2%B5%E8%92%82%E5%B2%A1%E6%99%A4%E6%95%99%E5%BB%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E5%8D%BF</a>"},{"pid":"076d9acf39c13778c195299db849c513210e2e31","tid":2217110,"uid":74339,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:20:00.000Z","msg":"梵蒂岡見錢開眼到幾乎背棄自己教義 希望見完之後佢哋會懸崖勒馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1def5fc78d486bd0aabca346f095fd10e55b1e","tid":2217110,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43589fe1a469af66e72940920f0e462d8907d7c","tid":2217110,"uid":8014,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"想睇下佢有咩招數可以令梵蒂岡變硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0156ae4809ea1d6c7736dea9502f0a7cb5c39c","tid":2217110,"uid":36040,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"去台灣好過啦"},{"pid":"fd754fe41c60c5c39c12290552359e6da1bf1ce4","tid":2217110,"uid":167597,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"對依班撚樣好失望"},{"pid":"558dfe29fecce6589e168f0e9aba6f72d467c2d6","tid":2217110,"uid":759,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"d43589fe1a469af66e72940920f0e462d8907d7c","tid":2217110,"uid":8014,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"想睇下佢有咩招數可以令梵蒂岡變硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl